    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "哈尔出现在眺望王都的法尔艾斯\\n和贝维特面前并探听二人的真正目的。\\n法尔艾斯则看透了哈尔故意败给\\n王子一行人的真相，反问其意图。\\n笑而不答的哈尔转身离去。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "嘿呀！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第七王子派首领",
            "context": "唔……坚持住！\\n拯救王都的将是我们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120127_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第七王子派士兵",
            "context": "喂，快看！\\n王城的浓雾散去了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第七王子派首领",
            "context": "那是……原来如此！\\n一定是尤蒂尔大人\\n打倒了魔神！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第七王子派首领",
            "context": "大伙，魔神已经被打败了！\\n我们也赶快收拾掉\\n这些帝国军吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "该死，敌军势头又起来了！\\n哈尔大人！请下达指示……\\n嗯？哈尔大人去哪儿了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "那个……从刚才起\\n就不见了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "该、该死……那个男人！\\n我一直就觉得他不可信！\\n究竟逃到哪里去了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "从这里看过去，王都也不过\\n是个渺小的玩具呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "空负盛名、徒有其表的都城。\\n就跟那个第七王子一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "这是最近能眺望王都的最后机会了。\\n失去了执政者，\\n索尔·阿尔贝里亚前途堪忧呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "哥哥……谢谢你，\\n这座城市我已经很了解了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "是吗？\\n那我们走吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "嗯，但在此之前……\\n躲在那边的人，不用管吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "噢，你说他啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "呵呵，真是名不虚传。\\n果然发现了吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "请原谅我偷听二位的谈话。\\n能在此偶遇二位真是荣幸。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "哥哥……他是谁？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "他叫哈尔。以前担任过\\n王都守卫队队长。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "终于见到您了，\\n贝维特大人。\\n今后还请多多关照。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "话说回来，不顾自身安危\\n也要救出被囚禁的弟弟，\\n这样的哥哥着实令人钦佩呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "究竟是什么东西在驱使着\\n法尔艾斯大人呢。感觉不仅是\\n因为高洁的兄弟情义吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "哎呀，我一不小心多嘴了呢。\\n这只是我的一点拙见，\\n希望您别介意。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "看样子，这个人也不像是\\n站在我们这边的呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "莫非他打算阻挠我们？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "贝维特，没事的。\\n他不会威胁到我们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "好吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "感谢您息怒，\\n贝维特大人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "哈尔，看起来\\n你才有什么企图吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "喔，您的意思是？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "用魔导兵器守卫城墙\\n可谈不上万无一失。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你要是认真起来，\\n应该至少会准备\\n两三条计策才对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "您看了那场战斗吗。\\n我水平有限，才让新阿尔贝里亚军\\n突破入城，真是无地自容。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "原来如此。\\n那我还有一个问题，\\n叛军又是怎么回事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你精通谍报与谋略，\\n不会连自己军队内部的叛乱\\n都觉察不到吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "也可以认为是你\\n故意睁一只眼闭一只眼，\\n好让我弟弟一行人进入王城。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "法尔艾斯大人，您可真会说笑。\\n我这样的凡夫俗子\\n能干出什么来？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "我不过是一介\\n仰仗着王族这棵大树的\\n无能骑士罢了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "这就怪了。你所仰仗的\\n应该并不是王族吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "……\\n哎呀，这可真是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "什么都骗不过\\n法尔艾斯大人的慧眼呢。\\n呵呵，真是越来越令人期待了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "那就让我好好欣赏\\n二位的表演吧。\\n我们有缘再会……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "就这么放他走没问题吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "嗯。因为他的“能力”\\n将来说不定能在\\n我的研究中派上用场。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "好了，我们也不能这样下去，\\n推进自己的计划吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "嗯，是啊，哥哥。\\n我们还有好多事要做呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_14_10_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}